#' Launch the APC Dashboard Application
#'
#' This function launches the APC Dashboard Shiny application, with various options for production, report generation,
#' and Perforce file handling.
#'
#' @param precomputeData Logical. Whether to precompute data before launching. Default is `TRUE`.
#' @param isProduction Logical. Flag to indicate if the app is running in production mode. Default is `FALSE`.
#' @param generateAPCReport Logical. Whether to generate the APC report. Default is `FALSE`.
#' @param APCReportZoomfactor Numeric. Zoom factor for the APC report. Default is `0.615`.
#' @param checkoutPerforceFiles Logical. Whether to checkout files from Perforce. Default is `FALSE`.
#' @param changelistDescription Character. Description for Perforce changelist. Default is `"Updated APC Dashboard as of <current date>"`.
#' @param deployment Character. Deployment environment, either `"server"` or `"local"`.
#' @param pathToProjectDir Character. Path to the project directory. Default is current working directory (`getwd()`).
#' @param manualInputDataPaths List or NULL. Optional manually provided data paths. Default is `NULL`.
#' @param hostedPort Integer. Port to host the Shiny app on. Default is `9999`.
#' @param buildPCCReportout Logical. Whether to build the PCC Report output. Default is `FALSE`.
#' @param test Logical. Flag for test mode. Default is `FALSE`.
#' @param temp Logical. Flag for using temporary data. Default is `FALSE`.
#' @param loadApp Logical. Whether to load the Shiny app after setup. Default is `TRUE`.
#' @param PCCReportOutStartDate Date. Start date for the PCC Report output. Default is `as.Date("2021-11-01")`.
#' @param PCCReportOutEndDate Date. End date for the PCC Report output. Default is `as.Date("2021-12-31")`.
#' @param PCCReportOutGenDate Date. Generation date for the PCC Report output. Default is `as.Date("2022-01-28")`.
#' @param browserpath Character or NULL. Path to the browser executable to launch the app. Default is `NULL`.
#'
#' @return None. The function launches the Shiny dashboard or performs report generation depending on parameters.
#' @export
#'
#' @examples
#' LaunchAPCDashboard(isProduction = TRUE, deployment = "local")